    <item>
      <title>Ziyi Chang</title>
      <link>https://zhoukanglei.github.io/people/ziyi-chang/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zhoukanglei.github.io/people/ziyi-chang/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;biography&#34;&gt;Biography&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ziyi Chang is a postdoctoral researcher at Inria Rennes, focusing on multi-character, multi-agent, and crowd modelling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;research-interests&#34;&gt;Research Interests&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Character animation and multi-character interaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Human modelling, diffusion models, and adversarial robustness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spatial-temporal modelling and generative models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
